cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with object viewpoint estimation from 2D images, which is a task in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of 3D models, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper proposes a novel CNN specifically tailored for the viewpoint estimation task, which indicates that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.LG (Machine Learning).
